room_title: Escape room "Bad Medicine" by Ace of Escape in Tucson
room_description: You've been in an accident, unable to identify yourself, you are sent to Dr. Mzrahi for observation and holding. You quickly realize the doctor has ill intentions and become desperate to escape. Luckily for you, there's a nurse at the nursing station you can call for help, but she doesn't want to get caught. The doctor will return in 65 minutes and you better not be here!
